description: Molo's Miami Grill is run by a Husband & Wife team with 30+ years in the service industry. Mike our Chef has combined a popular twist on local favorites, Such as our homemade Cuban sandwich, fresh made Empanadas, Fried Mac & Cheese Balls, Caribbean Jerk Chicken with Fresh Coconut Rice & Black Beans, Blackened Fish of the day with freshmade Chutney. Made to order Veggie Spring Rolls and daily fresh specials!
name: Molo's Miami Grill
